itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"四十幾歲未到人老珠黃嗰時香咗咪啱囉，又可以娶過個新皇后<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4571db53e7075181e919c4472b2f4c62e4f0787f","tid":1015610,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0cf7534c2b0cc3151b549add29fb52943ffb337","tid":1015610,"uid":6111,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"根本好多病都要開刀做手術<br />\n就好似最普通既割盲腸咁<br />\n中醫可以點搞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"咩病都係執劑藥嘅啫"},{"pid":"5dfaee563e8407f8da39fd69ad903538a048ee75","tid":1015610,"uid":191926,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:08:16.000Z","msg":"一堆皇子，公主早夭<br />\n<br />\n好像孫登早死<br />\n明孝宗食錯藥<br />\n<br />\n不過公道小小講<br />\n中世紀西醫都係唔惦<br />\n<br />\n亨利五世 小小病就死左<br />\n如果唔係<br />\n可能今日無法國呢個國家"},{"pid":"05f8c319dbc8cf5bd9d6c4cb9d41a7e2ddf6ed08","tid":1015610,"uid":137217,"like":16,"dislike":5,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:17:04.000Z","msg":"公道啲講<br />\n西醫去到18世紀仲玩緊放血療法<br />\n中醫就成千幾年前已經有調理內息呢啲野<br />\n西醫都係有左顯微鏡有細菌學之後先真正開始醫到人<br />\n講緊既都係近百幾年內既事<br />\n其實古代中國好多野真係好先進<br />\n中國係比儒學玩死(儒學放係現代用就ok,但古代就會搞到打仗唔夠人打,最終咁多次打大仗都輸)<br />\n加上清呢啲垃圾更加唔洗講<br />\n最後加埋共產黨<br />\n中國呢世都唔洗旨意爬番頭<br />\n無好似埃及果啲咁從此收皮都算係咁"},{"pid":"0f24d898e43135b2f9af76296e6234846d6ac47f","tid":1015610,"uid":151833,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"皇宮就係中醫勁先搞個個神不知鬼不覺咁香左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常人食屎都唔會40歲就香啦"},{"pid":"f5fa46c46e633a3653d523314847ad7b754bbb7c","tid":1015610,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"我想知中國以前跌斷手腳可以點醫<br />\n<br />\n而家都要X光CT再開刀裝螺絲再加抗生素防止感染,唔好同我講以前睇下跌打裝下夾版就可以慢慢好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中醫係現代醫學前面最多只可以做輔助治療既角度, 可以係成個醫療系統既一part但無可能完全自成一角"},{"pid":"876c72d33c703b6dd831ad9fce3ca2ef5bfe3f37","tid":1015610,"uid":175192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"跌斷手腳好似係用兩塊木板夾住就會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中醫乜野病都係會叫你訓喺床度好好休息 好似係"},{"pid":"6e98331486a42d1554137be358383fe7780baac7","tid":1015610,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e1f5dfc357bdf2037b5ccbc969daf27e11d99dd","tid":1015610,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"了解下以前既西醫先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3cd7e57724a2ec46c24aacd3f1948bfbc80fc5","tid":1015610,"uid":84104,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:56:02.000Z","msg":"好似話以前啲人早死係因為佢地成日近親繁殖<br />\n引致好多細路一出世就有先天性病<br />\n皇室食咁撚多山珍海味<br />\n三高咪早死囉<br />\n生cancer都無得醫啦"},{"pid":"6470757ec5e87ad374a52177656da44901796e4c","tid":1015610,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4571db53e7075181e919c4472b2f4c62e4f0787f","tid":1015610,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0cf7534c2b0cc3151b549add29fb52943ffb337","tid":1015610,"uid":6111,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"根本好多病都要開刀做手術<br />\n就好似最普通既割盲腸咁<br />\n中醫可以點搞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"咩病都係執劑藥嘅啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f22be1f01f1edf08134704ff49761b06483016","tid":1015610,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f565073b807bc18b2241720e661353c97f1714","tid":1015610,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"真正皇后死